name: Verify From,Till,Type,Primary Contact Number and Reason for outing are mandatory fields

testSteps.description: 1: Verify From,Till,Type,Primary Contact Number and Reason for outing are mandatory fields ({parentTab=Leave Management, childTab=Apply, tab=Out Duty/Tour, heading=Apply Leave / WFH / Comp Off / Out Duty / Change Request})

children.description: Given User is logged into MIS
When User is on MIS Home Page
When User clicks on "Apply" sub tab of "Leave Management" tab
And Verify "Apply Leave / WFH / Comp Off / Out Duty / Change Request" of "Apply" tab
When User clicks on "Out Duty/Tour" Tab
Then Click on Submit button for Out of Duty Tab
Then Verify "Outing From,Outing Till" calendar is mandatory field
